{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_vrtx_01V5fgKyFhjh4bzSx4h8TuV9","type":"tool_result","content":"File created successfully at: /Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizm-docs/bot.prizm"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1825d45b-0e87-4048-aee3-8c65afe6c801","uuid":"2bf90766-ef30-485a-a55f-0140fcbf218c","timestamp":"2026-03-22T06:49:53.796Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"create","filePath":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizm-docs/bot.prizm","content":"MODULE: src/bot\nFILES: 8 (+30 command handlers in commands/handlers/)\nRESPONSIBILITY: Telegram bot — message handling, command routing, file delivery, streaming output\nINTERFACES:\n- createTelegramBot(): Promise<Telegraf> — initialize bot with all command handlers and services\n- bot._f018.subscribeCrossChannel(chatId): void — subscribe realtimeHub for cross-channel push\nKEY_FILES:\n- telegram.js: Main bot setup, text handler, file handling, stream publisher (~1013 lines)\n- commands/index.js: Command registry and routing\n- commands/help.js: Help text generation\nDEPENDENCIES:\n- uses: telegraf: Telegram bot framework\n- imports: src/services/ai-cli-service.js: executeAiCli, interruptAiCli\n- imports: src/services/message-router.js: F-018 unified message routing\n- imports: src/services/session-bind.js: F-018 session binding for cross-channel\n- imports: src/services/realtime-hub.js: F-018 event subscription for cross-channel push\n- imports: src/services/session-store.js: session state\n- imports: src/services/chat-service.js: legacy (still imported for /reset command)\nTRAPS:\n- Telegram bot text handler uses messageRouter.processMessage() (F-018) — no longer calls executeAiCli directly\n- Cross-channel push only subscribes for bindings that exist at bot startup; dynamic bindings via API need manual subscribeCrossChannel() call\n- Heartbeat progress messages disabled after F-018 migration to messageRouter (messageRouter lacks onHeartbeat hook)\n- bot._f018 is an internal namespace — not a stable public API\nUPDATED: 2026-03-22\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
