{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_vrtx_01XcnR8LY84CxAagZoZbR2Kf","type":"tool_result","content":"File created successfully at: /Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizm-docs/routes.prizm"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1825d45b-0e87-4048-aee3-8c65afe6c801","uuid":"47d340b1-5d1e-4591-b711-9423e3ab2e91","timestamp":"2026-03-22T06:49:53.799Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"create","filePath":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizm-docs/routes.prizm","content":"MODULE: src/routes\nFILES: 1\nRESPONSIBILITY: HTTP API route definitions — chat, SSE events, session binding, screenshots, system exec\nINTERFACES:\n- createApiRouter({realtimeHub, sessionBind, messageRouter, sessionStore}): Router\n- POST /api/bind: bind web session to Telegram chat ID\n- POST /api/unbind: remove session binding\n- GET /api/bindings: query bindings (all or by webSessionId)\n- GET /api/events: SSE stream with message history replay on connect\n- POST /api/chat: send message via unified messageRouter\n- POST /api/chat/reset: clear session state\n- POST /api/screenshot: capture screenshot\n- POST /api/system/exec: execute system command\nKEY_FILES:\n- api-routes.js: All API endpoints (~200 lines)\nDEPENDENCIES:\n- uses: express: Router\n- imports: src/services/chat-service.js: buildSessionContext (for SSE key building)\n- imports: src/services/screenshot-service.js: captureScreenshot\n- imports: src/services/system-exec-service.js: executeSystemCommand\nTRAPS:\n- All F-018 endpoints (bind/unbind/bindings/chat/reset) call await sessionBind.ensureReady() — must await before calling sync methods\n- /api/events replays full message history on connect (AC6 offline sync) — could be large for long sessions\n- No authentication on bind/unbind endpoints (consistent with project pattern but security concern for production)\nUPDATED: 2026-03-22\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
